\vec{a}, \vec{b} , \vec{c} 
\mathbb{R}^3 
f:\mathbb{R}^3 \to \mathbb{R}
(x,y,z)
 \Big( \frac{\partial f}{\partial \vec{a} } \Big)^2 +\Big( \frac{\partial f}{\partial \vec{b} } \Big)^2 +\Big( \frac{\partial f}{\partial \vec{c} } \Big)^2  = \Big( \frac{\partial f}{\partial {x} } \Big)^2 + \Big( \frac{\partial f}{\partial {y} } \Big)^2+\Big( \frac{\partial f}{\partial {z} } \Big)^2
a=(a_1,a_2,a_3)
b=(b_1,b_2,b_3)
c=(c_1,c_2,c_3)
UU^T=I
U
 \frac{\partial f}{\partial a}=a_1\frac{\partial f}{\partial x}+ a_2\frac{\partial f}{\partial y}+ a_3\frac{\partial f}{\partial z} 
 \frac{\partial f}{\partial b}=b_1\frac{\partial f}{\partial x}+ b_2\frac{\partial f}{\partial y}+ b_3\frac{\partial f}{\partial z} 
 \frac{\partial f}{\partial c}=c_1\frac{\partial f}{\partial x}+ c_2\frac{\partial f}{\partial y}+ c_3\frac{\partial f}{\partial z} 
 \nabla_{a,b,c}\ f=U\nabla_{x,y,z}\ f, 
 U=\left(\begin{matrix}a_1 & a_2 & a_3 \\ b_1 & b_2 & b_3 \\ c_1 & c_2 & c_3 \end{matrix}\right) 
